snippet.textDisplay: I know a lot of people won't agree with me but this should be national anthem of Pakistan. Not the coke studio version but this is beautiful. Our current national anthem is in Persian and I am sure not half the people know the words and close to 80% don't know the meaning of those words. National anthem should be in local common language and should be recited with pride.

snippet.textDisplay: It's a splendid performance of well known artists, specially Farida khanum shahiba, and all other great figures. But if something is missing, that is madam Shahnaz Begum ! Who made this song immortal. She is not in the video and she is not even mentioned for a second, who delivered this wonderful naghma to every person who love their country so much. It is unfortunate not to mention her name who made this song even more beautiful.
